    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_3706765268941581368.png",
                "id": "talent4718",
                "key": "西風劍術·女僕",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "西風劍術·女僕"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護體岩鎧</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護體岩鎧</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>為我方出戰角色提供<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">2點護盾</span>。</p><p>此<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護盾</span>耗盡前，我方受到的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>減半。（無條件進位至整數）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/b1d7ce40985ba00be1cddb9ab8853acc_3664423239787528014.png",
                "id": "talent42492",
                "key": "護心鎧",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "護心鎧"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">大掃除</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">大掃除</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">角色使用普通攻擊時：</span>少花費一個<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>。（每回合一次）</p><p>角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">普通攻擊</span>造成的傷害+2，造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>變為<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/41a3e6172eedfcebb93941683385e926_9105287960191581613.png",
                "id": "talent65257",
                "key": "大掃除",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "大掃除"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（冰）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（水）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（火）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（雷）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_5145734239583727645.png",
                "id": "talent34274",
                "key": "岩元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護盾</span></strong></p><p>此護盾所保護的角色受到傷害時，將會消耗護盾來抵消傷害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合結束階段，持續回合-1；</p><p>持續回合耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8485695385823013342.png",
